data.name: Inception
data.description: Inception is a mind-bending sci-fi thriller about a group of thieves who enter the subconscious of their targets to steal secrets. The protagonist must plant an idea into the mind of a business mogul.

data.name: The Witcher
data.description: The Witcher is a fantasy series set in a medieval-inspired world, following Geralt of Rivia, a monster hunter who battles dark forces and faces moral dilemmas in a land full of political intrigue.
